nfcjlib.core

Class DESFireEV1.RawAuthentication

  • java.lang.Object
    • nfcjlib.core.DESFireEV1.RawAuthentication
  • Enclosing class:
    DESFireEV1

    public static class DESFireEV1.RawAuthentication
extends java.lang.Object
    Authentication done in two steps. Useful when actions have to be taken in between the message exchanges. Call start to execute the first step and end to execute the second step.

    randA: random number A
    randB: random number B
    randAr: random number A rotated
    randAre: random number A rotated and enciphered
    randBr: random number B rotated
    randABre: random numbers concatenated with B rotated and both enciphered
    randBe: random number B enciphered
